"content": "<h2>Hail as destructive</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:11\">JOS 10:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:11-Ezek13:13\">EZK 13:11–13:13</a></p>\n<h2>Hail as a sign of the power of God</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:22-Job38:23\">JOB 38:22–38:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:32\">PSA 105:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:17-Ps147:18\">PSA 147:17–147:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:2\">ISA 28:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:17\">HAG 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Hail as one of the ten plagues of Egypt</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:18-Exod9:33\">EXO 9:18–9:33</a></p>\n<h2>Hail as an aspect of the final divine judgment</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:7\">REV 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:19\">REV 11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:21\">REV 16:21</a></p>",
